Thanks @dave-msk.

@martinwicke  This is fine. I prefer device_fn over ps_strategy due to the fact that device_fn is more general but ps_strategy assumes ps is not the cluster.

However, it will be user's own risk to debug this. device_fn or ps_strategy is not easy to write.
